author: Jennifer Miller
title: Fire rages at Quincy Point marina
text:
A raging fire has engulfed several boats at Cove Way in Quincy this morning.
The Boston Fire Department, Quincy Fire Department and Quincy Police Marine Unit are all on scene at the Quincy Point blaze. At least three boats could be seen burning when the blaze broke out around 7:30 a.m. today.
Authorities were towing boats to safety, away from the towering flames.
